               stealing, on the <rs id="t18261207-267-cd1550" type="crimeDate">8th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261207-267-off1549 t18261207-267-cd1550"></join>, one 10l. Bank note
            </rs>, the property of 
               <persName id="t18261207-267-victim1463" type="victimName">
                  George 
                  Jaques
               <interp inst="t18261207-267-victim1463" type="surname" value="Jaques"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18261207-267-victim1463" type="given" value="George"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18261207-267-victim1463" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261207-267-off1549 t18261207-267-victim1463"></join>
